  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TNT7">
<l>vaṟpuṭaiya varaineṭuntōḷ maṉṉar māḷa</l>
<l>vaṭivāya maḻuvēnti yulaka māṇṭu</l>
<l>veṟpuṭaiya neṭuṅkaṭaluḷ taṉivē luytta</l>
<l>vēḷmutalā veṉṟāṉūr vintai mēya</l>
<l>kaṟpuṭaiya maṭakkaṉṉi kāval pūṇṭa</l>
<l>kaṭipoḻilcūḻ neṭumaṟukil kamala vēli</l>
<l>poṟpuṭaiya malaiyaraiyaṉ paṇiya niṉṟa</l>
<l>pūṅkōva lūrttoḻutum pōtu neñcē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>[My] heart, go forth; let us worship [him] in lush Kōvalūr,</l>
<l rend="indent">with lotus borders on long streets surrounded by fragrant groves,</l>
<l>Which endures for the king of [the people of] the magnificent mountains to worship,</l>
<l rend="indent">where the chaste, simple virgin who dwells in the Vindhyas</l>
<l>Undertook protection of the city of him who, ruling the world bearing a curved axe</l>
<l rend="indent">so that kings with strong mountain[-like], high shoulders would die,</l>
<l>Conquered first [among others] the youth who threw</l>
<l rend="indent">a singular spear in the wide sea with mountains.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
